</li><li>Change the order using the Up or Down arrows or by typing the order number and pressing the Save Order icon. The Modules will display in the new order within the Position.
</li></ul>
</li><li>You can open a Module for editing by clicking on the Module Name. This opens the <a href="<?php echo Route::url('index.php?option=com_help&view=help&keyref=Screen.modules.edit.15'); ?>" title="Screen.modules.edit.15" class="mw-redirect">Module Manager - New/Edit</a> screen.
</li></ul>
